{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/12-backspace-string-compare/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soobing","author":"[Soobin Bak]","siteUrl":"https://soobing.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"soobing/soobing.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"soobing"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b4369288-1927-5bb1-81cb-1f828ae4910c","excerpt":"어제 문제만 풀고 포스팅을 못해서 잔디를 못심었네 ㅠㅠ 속상☔️ 오늘 문제는 easy 문제라서 그런지 쉽고 빠르게 풀 수 있었다. (easy를 풀때는 언제나 즐겁지요~~~)  문제 요약 문제에서 두개의 string…","html":"<p>어제 문제만 풀고 포스팅을 못해서 잔디를 못심었네 ㅠㅠ 속상☔️ 오늘 <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/backspace-string-compare/\">문제</a>는 easy 문제라서 그런지 쉽고 빠르게 풀 수 있었다. (easy를 풀때는 언제나 즐겁지요~~~)</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"backspace string compare\"\n        title=\"backspace string compare\"\n        src=\"/static/cb7967ab8de5a1e4df5e7bd50b974ef7/e5166/backspace-string-compare.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cb7967ab8de5a1e4df5e7bd50b974ef7/f93b5/backspace-string-compare.jpg 300w,\n/static/cb7967ab8de5a1e4df5e7bd50b974ef7/b4294/backspace-string-compare.jpg 600w,\n/static/cb7967ab8de5a1e4df5e7bd50b974ef7/e5166/backspace-string-compare.jpg 1200w,\n/static/cb7967ab8de5a1e4df5e7bd50b974ef7/45687/backspace-string-compare.jpg 1262w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"문제 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 요약</h1>\n<p>문제에서 두개의 string이 주어진다.\n각 문자열에는 #가 포함되어있다. 이것은 백스페이스를 의미해서 바로 앞의 글자를 지우는 역할을 하는데\n글자를 지우고 남은 결과가 같은지 확인하는 문제이다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"문제 해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 해결</h1>\n<p>일단 순회를 해야하는데 뒤에서 부터 순회를 할꺼다.(백스페이스 니까) 그리고 #가 나오면 그 갯수를 카운팅하고 #가 아닐 경우 백스페이스(#)의 갯수가 0개이면 해당 문자는 지워질 수 없으니 저장하는 방식으로 구현했다.\ninput으로 주어진 두 개의 문자열을 위의 방법대로 각각 돌려보고 그 결과를 비교해보면 된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-traverse-and-get-length-and-then-traverse-again\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-traverse-and-get-length-and-then-traverse-again\" aria-label=\"1 traverse and get length and then traverse again permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1) Traverse and Get Length and then Traverse again</h2>\n<p>링크드리스트의 길이는 전체를 순회하는 수 밖에 없다. 그런 다음 다시 반만큼 순회하여 그 노드를 리턴하면 된다고 생각했다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>시간 복잡도: O(N + M)</li>\n<li>공간 복잡도: O(1)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>문제에서 제시하는 솔루션은 나와 비슷해서 패스~</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * @param {string} S\n * @param {string} T\n * @return {boolean}\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">getString</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">str</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> erasedStr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">>=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> count<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>count <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> erasedStr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> str<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> erasedStr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> count<span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> erasedStr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">backspaceCompare</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token constant\">S</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token constant\">T</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">getString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">S</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token function\">getString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"소감\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%90\" aria-label=\"소감 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>소감</h2>\n<p>진짜 잘하는 사랆들 보면 코드가 정말 심플하던데 나도 그렇게 하고싶다 🧞‍♂️</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"🌬Backspace String Compare","date":"April 10, 2020","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/cb7967ab8de5a1e4df5e7bd50b974ef7/14b42/backspace-string-compare.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/12-backspace-string-compare/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/11-middle-of-the-linked-list/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"💊Middle of the Linked List","category":"algorithm","draft":false}},"next":null}}}